# Changelog
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [0.0.6] - 02.02.2021
### Changed
    - Pattern 'Singleton' applied to blockchain

## [0.0.5] - 29.01.2021
### Changed
    - Block generation is delegated to the miner

## [0.0.4] - 18.01.2021
### Added
    - Added lombok

## [0.0.3] - 16.01.2021
### Added
    - Added time of creation in block(Issue #2)
    - Added blockchain serialization (Issue #2)
    - Added 'proof of work' solution with magic number in block(Issue #2)
### Changed
    - Block[] -> LinkedList<Block>
## [0.0.2] - 10.01.2021
### Added
    - Added chain check (Issue #1)

## [0.0.1] - 10.01.2021
### Added
    - Implemented adding 10 blocks to blockchain (Issue #1)